{"an6.120-139:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 6.120–139 ","an6.120-139:0.2":"12. Samannavagga ","an6.120-139:0.3":"Bhallikadisutta ","an6.120-139:1.1":"“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannagato bhalliko gahapati …pe… ","an6.120-139:1.2":"sudatto gahapati anathapindiko … ","an6.120-139:1.3":"citto gahapati macchikasandiko … ","an6.120-139:1.4":"hatthako alavako … ","an6.120-139:1.5":"mahanamo sakko … ","an6.120-139:1.6":"uggo gahapati vesaliko … ","an6.120-139:1.7":"uggato gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.8":"surambattho … ","an6.120-139:1.9":"jivako komarabhacco … ","an6.120-139:1.10":"nakulapita gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.11":"tavakanniko gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.12":"purano gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.13":"isidatto gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.14":"sandhano gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.15":"vicayo gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.16":"vijayamahiko gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.17":"mendako gahapati … ","an6.120-139:1.18":"vasettho upasako … ","an6.120-139:1.19":"arittho upasako … ","an6.120-139:1.20":"saraggo upasako tathagate nitthangato amataddaso amatam sacchikatva iriyati. ","an6.120-139:1.21":"Katamehi chahi? ","an6.120-139:1.22":"Buddhe aveccappasadena, dhamme aveccappasadena, sanghe aveccappasadena, ariyena silena, ariyena nanena, ariyaya vimuttiya. ","an6.120-139:1.23":"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannagato saraggo upasako tathagate nitthangato amataddaso amatam sacchikatva iriyati”ti. ","an6.120-139:1.24":"Tevisatimam. ","an6.120-139:1.25":"Samannavaggo dvadasamo. "}